overview:
www.MYHEALTHJOBS.com ® is a leading career portal dedicated for healthcare professionals such as doctors, nurses, therapists and allied healthcare professionals. Healthcare job seekers can find employment opportunities nationwide. Portal provide easy job finding experience based on location and distance and search criteria. 

 Our primary goal is to make health care recruitment efficient using the second generation technology platform apart from the legacy e-recruitment. The underlying principal is to bubble up quality candidates using social and professional networks of healthcare professionals. This is in contrast to providing quantity of perhaps unsuitable candidates. &#8221;

MYHEALTHJOBS.com allows health care job seekers to share the jobs with their network, Tweet the jobs, chat with their prospective employers and use the tools provided to showcase their profile with optional video resume.

In final place, it must be added that the site has a true social aura since community features are included. In practice, this means that those who use it regularly can connect among themselves and also with prospective employers in order to start showcasing their skills.
